{"tid":991442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木 村 拓 哉與 竇靖童 在電車上尬舞","createTime":"2019-01-22T11:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T22:19:58.000Z","uid":215823,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a68e8d9ef8b25968ade771bd7d09b36db79f98c5","tid":991442,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/22/191839_39d0e61ef6b98b34b0277d1ed33d471e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2F191839_39d0e61ef6b98b34b0277d1ed33d471e.png&h=b5d74395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BC-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E6%8B%93%E5%93%89-x-%E7%AB%87%E9%9D%96%E7%AB%A5%E5%BE%AE%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4-055704311.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%258B%2593%25E5%2593%2589-x-%25E7%25AB%2587%25E9%259D%2596%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%2590%25B6%25E5%2585%2588%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B4-055704311.html&d=ah4jksLE9LN9r3P%2BgshA5Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=464313c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BC-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E6%8B%93%E5%93%89-x-%E7%AB%87%E9%9D%96%E7%AB%A5%E5%BE%AE%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4-055704311.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本天王木村拓哉合體王菲女兒竇靖童，兩人今天出席牛仔褲品牌的代言記者會，提到與竇靖童攜手，他笑說：「我跟她媽媽也合作過，心情真的很奇妙。」木村不僅誇她是個非常自然出色的人，記者會結束後，還與她搭肩扮鬼臉合照。<br />\n<br />\n木村拓哉從1994年起連續5年獲頒「日本牛仔褲大獎」，進入榮譽殿堂，這次再度為19年前代言過的牛仔褲品牌拍廣告，他表示，經過這麼多年，還可以被選為代言人真的很開心。"},{"pid":"0b13bec00c9bd5e8ba643ed89da90063b2b6805a","tid":991442,"uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf9099f526dcb3066bf05a20f6dfa2e1297191e","tid":991442,"uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"廣告中他與竇靖童在電車上尬舞，展現華麗舞技，他2004年時曾與王菲演出王家衛執導的《2046》．這次與竇靖童合體，他笑說：「很開心可以跟她合作，有種說不出的奇妙感受，因為我也認識她媽媽，這讓我深刻感受到時光歷程的轉變。」<br />\n<br />\n提起拍攝花絮，木村拓哉表示，雖然看來是在電車上，但其實他們是在攝影棚拍攝，廣告中他被竇靖童用中文嗆：「最近沒跳舞吧！」他在記者會上雖坦言說：「體力上的確有點負擔。」不過仍展現帥氣的吊環翻轉。"},{"pid":"d1690ffd60b0ffc92eee920d5ebc75e9ec0ab596","tid":991442,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"下巴線呢"},{"pid":"22342e97241f781614bfa6cdaff2739ae767754f","tid":991442,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"兩個男人？"},{"pid":"768d67705d130d586ca6bd1b3926d990a23e7fb1","tid":991442,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"個胸仲平過木村"},{"pid":"5be1960cbea4e88c41f485812a3517807ddb253d","tid":991442,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"得我覺得正?"},{"pid":"bd9e09155af0449c2e603880ef51b51779a8fcc1","tid":991442,"uid":63198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"幾好睇<br />\n不過一講蝗語即刻柒晒"},{"pid":"365b8c9afb87a77fff3a35adb4dbc7178c78ae8f","tid":991442,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"唔記得同王菲合作過咩"},{"pid":"12ff70b80a092dbdcb55088c090f7113ce0cb27b","tid":991442,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365b8c9afb87a77fff3a35adb4dbc7178c78ae8f","tid":991442,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"唔記得同王菲合作過咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"2046？"},{"pid":"93cb819efbe9e6b66abd4ab3e7a82e2044c62ea0","tid":991442,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"774464bde3409d149402b976a7378aeaca4ba1f9","tid":991442,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T21:31:14.000Z","msg":"木村呢個髮型好似後生好多"},{"pid":"05d78fe7ae8b8f0358b873d85983cdf41d36c01c","tid":991442,"uid":6058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T22:19:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢尬舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}